<abstract><t>This memo proposes an unbounded Flexible Address Space (FAS), consisting of a publicly routable Global Address Part (GP) and a locally routable Local Address Part (LP).  It expands GP and LP to provide address privacy and special LP formats.  Use cases are also provided.</t></abstract>

